      "unit_id": "p13_g02",
      "translation": "Since the onset of the pandemic, the Group's business teams have responded swiftly and actively assisted in mitigating the impact on our communities while ensuring employee safety. The Group has implemented a wide range of measures for this purpose, including financial support, provision of medical supplies, complimentary coverage, access to healthcare resources, streamlined service processes and accelerated claims payments, of which I am proud. We have, as always, identified every possible reason to make a claim payment, and have paid out over US$16 billion in insurance benefits and claims during the year, providing our customers with critically important financial protection."
